# InputReadoutSystem  (sbx)

## Purpose
Sole writer of LabelComponent. Returns early until the InputStateSingletonComponent is present.
Each frame it formats the live input state (mouse position, number of held keys, scroll offset)
into a string and writes it to the m_Text of every label tagged with InputReadoutTagComponent.

## Input Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| InputStateSingletonComponent | read | Source of mouse/key/scroll state; guard (returns early if absent) |
| InputReadoutTagComponent | read | Selects which labels to rewrite |
| LabelComponent | write | m_Text rewritten with the formatted input state |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| LabelComponent | write | m_Text set to the formatted input readout |
